name: Alice Example
headline: Master Quilter & Textile Artist
bio: Passionate about traditional quilting techniques and modern textile art. Love creating intricate patterns and teaching others the craft. Specialize in hand-stitched quilts and fabric collage.

name: Bella Example
headline: Embroidery Artist & Pattern Designer
bio: Creating beautiful hand-embroidered pieces and designing original patterns. Focus on botanical motifs and vintage-inspired designs. Always experimenting with new stitches and techniques.

name: Clara Example
headline: Knitting Instructor & Yarn Enthusiast
bio: Teaching knitting to beginners and creating complex cable patterns. Passionate about sustainable yarns and helping others discover the joy of knitting. Love designing cozy sweaters and accessories.

name: Diana Example
headline: Full Stack Developer & Open Source Contributor
bio: Building web applications with React, Node.js, and TypeScript. Passionate about clean code, testing, and contributing to open source projects. Love teaching programming concepts to beginners.

name: Ella Example
headline: DevOps Engineer & Cloud Architect
bio: Designing scalable cloud infrastructure and automating deployments. Expertise in AWS, Docker, and CI/CD pipelines. Always learning new technologies and sharing knowledge with the community.

name: Fiona Example
headline: UI/UX Designer & Frontend Developer
bio: Creating beautiful and intuitive user interfaces. Focus on accessibility, responsive design, and user-centered design principles. Love bringing designs to life with modern CSS and JavaScript.

name: George Example
headline: Furniture Maker & Woodworking Instructor
bio: Creating custom furniture pieces and teaching traditional woodworking techniques. Specialize in hand-tool work and joinery. Passionate about sustainable wood sourcing and preserving traditional crafts.

name: Henry Example
headline: Wood Turner & Lathe Specialist
bio: Creating beautiful turned bowls, vases, and decorative pieces. Focus on green wood turning and natural edge work. Love sharing techniques and helping others discover the art of wood turning.

name: Iris Example
headline: Fine Woodworker & Craftsperson
bio: Creating heirloom-quality furniture and small woodworking projects. Specialize in dovetail joints, hand-planed surfaces, and traditional finishing techniques. Always learning and refining skills.
